  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございまーす！！\n今日も一日、よろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning!\nLet’s all give our best today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7666666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、下の郵便受け\n色々溜まっていたので持ってきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ the mail downstairs\nwas piling up‚ so I brought it up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 5.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さくら、琴乃、おはよう。ありがとう……ん？\nこれプレタポルテからだ。中身は……ライブへの招待？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ Kotono‚ good morning. And thanks… hm?\nThis is from Pret-A-Porter. What’s inside… Tickets to a live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.457277043660483,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5423.9437103271675,
          "startTime": 16.4572770436605
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "あー！　そ、それは……今、超入手困難なBIG4\nスリクスのライブチケットですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahhh! Th-those are… tickets to the super-difficult-to-obtain\nBIG4 IIIX live!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスって、瑠依ちゃん達が移籍した事務所の？\nでも、なんで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX… as in‚ the group signed to the agency Rui-chan’s group transferred to?\nBut why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルも出る合同ライブらしいわね\nもしかして、瑠依さん達が招待を？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE is performing with them.\nMaybe Rui-san sent us these tickets.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、差出人は姫野さんって書いてあります……\n何かのいやーな作戦とかでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. The return address says it’s from Himeno-san.\nI can only assume it’s some nefarious plot?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "分からない。けど\nスリクスのパフォーマンスを見られる絶好の機会だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know.\nBut this is a great opportunity to watch IIIX perform.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "誘われたのなら、それに乗ってやろう\nチケットは七枚か。連れて行くとしたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were invited‚ so we should go.\nThere are seven tickets. Who should we take?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2633.333333333333,
          "startTime": 60.1
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6133.333333333333,
          "startTime": 66.23333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 65.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 65.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 66.2333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "うわ～！　すごいすご～い！\nめっちゃ盛り上がってるね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow! So cool!\nThis place is on fire!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 73.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "まだ開場まで二時間はあるのに\nもうこんなに外で待っているんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live doesn’t start for another two hours‚\nbut there’s already a massive line outside…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 78.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "とんでもない人気ですよね\n物販のために始発で来る人もいるみたいです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They really are crazy-popular.\nSome people even took the earliest train here to buy merch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 84.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "人が多過ぎて、クラクラしてきちゃうね……\n圧倒されちゃうなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are so many people‚ I’m getting dizzy.\nI feel overwhelmed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 90.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね\n時間があるなら、どこかで落ち着きたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah…\nIf we have time‚ I’d like to relax somewhere for a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 96.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "賛成です～。まさかと思いますけど、か弱い\n乙女達をここで二時間も待たせるなんてことは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I second that! I don’t suppose you intended to make\nus frail maidens stand outside two hours waiting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 104.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "しないしない。今、近くの店を探してる所だ\n確かに、早く着き過ぎちゃったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I don’t. I’m looking for a place right now.\nYou’re right. We did get here a little too early.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 111.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（しかし、分かってはいたけど、ここまでの人気とは）\n（BIG4の一角……さすがだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I already knew they were popular‚ but not this popular.）\n（I guess that’s the BIG4.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5200.000000000003,
          "startTime": 122.26666666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8333.333333333343,
          "startTime": 125.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 121.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 121.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_live-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 121.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "トリエルー！　おかえりー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE! Welcome back!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "瑠依ちゃーん！！　さいこー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan!!! You’re the best!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 127.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "す、凄い声援……さすが、トリエルだね\nちょっと、安心したかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wow‚ they’re loud… Way to go‚ TRINITYAiLE!\nI think I’m a bit relieved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 134.533333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "いろんなゴタゴタがあった後だものね\nでも、相変わらず沢山のファンに恵まれてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ after all the chaos they went through‚\nit’s good to see they’re still blessed with plenty of fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 141.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "わー！　瑠依ちゃーん、優ちゃーん、すみれちゃーん！\nかっこ良かったよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Woo-hoo! Go‚ Rui-chan! Go‚ Yu-chan! Go‚ Sumire-chan!\nYou were so awesome!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 150.13
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "こ、ここにも熱狂的なファンが……\nあの、芽衣さん。関係者席だからもう少し大人しく",
